member.remarks:
This endpoint generates sample error logs for the last 7 days to help with testing and demonstration. The dummy data includes various error types, severities, and priorities.
Sample response:
{ "message": "Successfully seeded 245 dummy logs", "logsGenerated": 245, "daysOfData": 7 }

This endpoint checks if the system already contains log data from the last 7 days. Useful for determining whether dummy data seeding is needed.
Sample response:
{ "hasData": true, "message": "System contains existing log data" }

